Interface ParticipantDTO

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Remote
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ParticipantDTOImpl

    public interface ParticipantDTO
extends Remote
    Remote-interface for participant data-transfer-object. ParticipantDTO is typically used to represent a participant at the client.
